g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來依家有咁嘅功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網揾過幾隻，但成3千銀，幾貴下<br />\n但問題係唔知部cam準唔準<br />\n最怕買左之後<br />\n有人行過左先開始影<br />\n如果係咁又係嘥錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885c5074c708d7da532cf21a0feb9423585cb21b","tid":115173,"uid":13656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:31:03.000Z","msg":"圍村不嬲唔可以笠亂泊車"},{"pid":"aa33d0a4c6ac3e5d05753e96357ef421dd176e01","tid":115173,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駁長火<br />\n<br />\n宜家好多 cam 都有 motion detection</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無用過<br />\n效果點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf6561c36860d1811bee6ce15de363a80489681","tid":115173,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圍村不嬲唔可以笠亂泊車</blockquote><br />\n有比錢租㗎，如果自己亂泊<br />\n比人攪，心甘命抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d603b3991286f4585ca3de10eb111a25c0c62f7","tid":115173,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"村停車場就叫個負責人裝cam啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（但你唔好將政府咪當做村專用，你條村窮撚到要收呢種錢就一定會得罪人）<br />\n<br />\n或者裝個種360度cam<br />\n不過你應該最盡都係得幾日記錄"},{"pid":"91e23881fe5d2f5bbbcfeffe808b29fcd9f44359","tid":115173,"uid":16046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"我記得之前有間整cctv 可以多角度影， 但唔記得左係邊間， 你地泊車果d夾錢裝返個囉～ <br />\n好似一set 2000蚊<br />\n幫你搵下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e75ed9200344b964c83fca88646113e3c6c8810","tid":115173,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n條友應該精神有問題，隔離左右合共9架車，都比人係唔同時間刮花過，住村屋，無cctv，報左警又無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唯一辦法係裝cam睇住部車</blockquote><br />\n宜家唸緊，村民圍內夾錢裝一部cam影<br />\n但又唔知點裝<br />\n裝車cam又驚影唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好易之麻, 你有車cam 咪買舊12V電池連接頭就裝得la.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未買車cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無咩型號推介，可以泊車有人行過就影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來依家有咁嘅功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網揾過幾隻，但成3千銀，幾貴下<br />\n但問題係唔知部cam準唔準<br />\n最怕買左之後<br />\n有人行過左先開始影<br />\n如果係咁又係嘥錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前後 cam 差不多啦"},{"pid":"6c256570aebb0c4669d91966bfb435aa894afa05","tid":115173,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>圍村不嬲唔可以笠亂泊車</blockquote><br />\n有比錢租㗎，如果自己亂泊<br />\n比人攪，心甘命抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班陀地沒幫手睇住既咩"},{"pid":"482269b81832b96c8ecb6b9c125b474ebba4409d","tid":115173,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>村停車場就叫個負責人裝cam啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（但你唔好將政府咪當做村專用，你條村窮撚到要收呢種錢就一定會得罪人）<br />\n<br />\n或者裝個種360度cam<br />\n不過你應該最盡都係得幾日記錄</blockquote><br />\n宜家傾緊，睇下邊個夾錢裝<br />\n360 車cam?"},{"pid":"0de18234a91e8841c6f94fce427bfe5e5d2ffa12","tid":115173,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得之前有間整cctv 可以多角度影， 但唔記得左係邊間， 你地泊車果d夾錢裝返個囉～ <br />\n好似一set 2000蚊<br />\n幫你搵下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" clas